 shadow-[#D97706]/30">3</span><span data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:179:20" data-component-name="span" class="text-[#1C1208] text-base font-medium">Lock dates using a group poll</span></li><li data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:177:18" data-component-name="li" class="flex items-center gap-4"><span data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:178:20" data-component-name="span" class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white font-black text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm shadow-[#D97706]/30">4</span><span data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:179:20" data-component-name="span" class="text-[#1C1208] text-base font-medium">Set a realistic budget range</span></li><li data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:177:18" data-component-name="li" class="flex items-center gap-4"><span data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:178:20" data-component-name="span" class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white font-black text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm shadow-[#D97706]/30">5</span><span data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:179:20" data-component-name="span" class="text-[#1C1208] text-base font-medium">Build a shared itinerary</span></li><li data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:177:18" data-component-name="li" class="flex items-center gap-4"><span data-replit-metadata="artifacts/tryps-landing/src/pages/blog/how-to-plan-group-trip.tsx:178:20" data-component-name="span" class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white font-black text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm shadow-[#D97706]/30">6</span><span data-replit